title: Jim Rohn SuperPack
description:
Unique Collection. The biggest ever collection of self-help materials from Jim Rohn, audiobooks, videos and PDF ebooks. Nowhere else will you find such a unique, enormous collection of clear sounding materials from Jim. Everyhing is here from him. See also Anthony Robbins SuperPack, Robert Kiyosaki SuperPack and Success Party Advanced SuperPack. 

Seed it and share it! <3 The world needs your help! Let's create abundance!
